flowchart TD
    T_EMAIL[Trigger: Email Opened]
    T_SCORE[Trigger: Score Threshold]
    T_CONTACT[Trigger: Contact Created]

    A_SEND[Send Email]
    A_WAIT[Wait]
    D_COND{Condition?}
    A_UPDATE[Update Score]
    A_ADDTAG[Add Tag]
    E_END[End]

    T_EMAIL --> A_SEND
    T_SCORE --> A_SEND
    T_CONTACT --> A_SEND

    A_SEND --> A_WAIT
    A_WAIT --> D_COND

    D_COND -- Yes --> A_ADDTAG
    D_COND -- No --> A_UPDATE

    A_ADDTAG --> A_UPDATE
    A_UPDATE --> E_END